{"article_id":"hNeDRPcua6AOBjmz","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Trump , on the heels of his historic summit with Kim Jong Un , told Fox News ' Sean Hannity","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that he believes","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"the North Korean leader will begin to work toward dismantling his country ' s nuclear program \" virtually immediately . \"","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"The president left Singapore","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"after the two leaders signed a document","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"stating","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Pyongyang would work toward `` complete denuclearization of the Korean Peninsula . ''","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"In an interview with Fox News , Trump said","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"the process is \" really moving rapidly . \"","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" I just think","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"that we are now we are going to start the process of denuclearization of North Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"and I believe","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"that he ' s going back","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and will start it virtually immediately -","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"and he ' s already indicated that","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"and you look at what he ' s done , \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"WATCH THE FULL INTERVIEW WITH TRUMP ON FOX NEWS ' ' HANNITY ' AT 9 PM ET ON TUESDAY","depth":2},{"id":18,"text":"The historic agreement came","depth":4},{"id":19,"text":"after the two leaders held several meetings throughout the day .","depth":4},{"id":20,"text":"Trump was asked by a reporter","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"if Kim agreed to denuclearize","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"and he said ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" We are starting that process very quickly . \"","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Trump said at a press conference","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that he will be ending joint military exercises between the United States and South Korea .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"He also said","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Kim agreed to destroy a \" major \" missile testing site ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"but did not offer specific details .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"The joint declaration states","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"that the U.S. has committed to providing `` security guarantees '' to Pyongyang .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Whether the unpredictable North Korean leader will follow through remains unclear ,","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"but Trump sounded optimistic","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"as he left the summit .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"He told \" Hannity \"","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"the two of them \" got along from the beginning \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"and Kim understood the need","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"to dismantle his nuclear program .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"\" His country has to be de-nuked","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"and he understood that ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"he fully understood that ,","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"he didn ' t fight it , \"","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Trump said .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"The summit ,","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"which almost didn ' t happen ,","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"represented a remarkable turnaround from the tension between Washington and Pyongyang last summer","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"when Trump and Kim exchanged a war of words ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"with the American president warning the dictator of \" fire and fury . \"","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"Trump told Fox News , though ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"\" without the rhetoric","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"we wouldn ' t have been here . \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"\" So I think","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"the rhetoric ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"I hated to do it ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"sometimes I felt foolish","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"doing it ,","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"but we had no choice , \"","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"he said .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"As for what happens next ,","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"Trump insisted ,","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"\" I think","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"he ' s gone back to get this done .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"He wants to get it done . \"","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"During a gaggle later in the day with reporters on Air Force One , Trump said","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"he trusts Kim","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"but the U.S. would have to `` check ''","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"to ensure","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"denuclearization occurs .","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"`` We 're going to have to check him .","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"And we will check him ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"we 'll check him very strongly .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"But he has a plan total and complete , ''","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"`` He 's got a total plan .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"It will get done . ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"When asked whether he had any concerns about Kim ,","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"the president insisted","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Kim `` wants to get it done . ''","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"He added :","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"`` And we should all want that to happen . ''","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":161,"left":98,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":97,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":83,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":83,"left":0,"right":82,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":82,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":88,"right":95,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":88,"left":86,"right":87,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":86,"left":3,"right":85,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":85,"left":4,"right":84,"relation":"elabor